175 A.3d 174 MELISSA KOLLAR, PETITIONER-PETITIONER, v. BOARD OF EDUCATION OF THE TOWN OF HARRISON, HUDSON COUNTY, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT. (COMMISSIONER OF EDUCATION-RESPONDENT)

C-967 September Term 2017

079983 November 29, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005203-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
